-- France Says It Will File Brief Supporting Argentina in Debt Case
-- B y   S a n d r i n e   R a s t e l l o
-- 2013-07-26T19:28:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-26/france-says-it-will-file-brief-supporting-argentina-in-debt-case.html
France  will file a brief with the
U.S. Supreme Court in support of Argentina in a legal battle
over defaulted Argentine debt, the French finance ministry said
today in an e-mailed statement.  In the statement, the ministry said France is doing so to
preserve international financial stability.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sandrine Rastello in Washington at 
 srastello@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
